In this project i would be creating a game on mensuration of shapes.
the game would be centered on five basic shapes, which include
a triangle, square, circle, rectangle and trapezium.

The game is to calculate the area or perimeter of any of the given shapes.

There will be 5 options which stand for the shapes above.
when the user chooses any of the options, they will have to provide the dimensions for any of the given calculation.